{"tid":910594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：65%年長人士曾使用流動支付","createTime":"2018-11-21T09:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T11:09:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c096d75e20701b486218ead85012e32e7e91188f","tid":910594,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2210000/2213439/payment_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2210000%2F2213439%2Fpayment_1024.jpg&h=983abbdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n證監會附屬機構投資者教育中心調查發現，65%受訪者過去12個月内曾使用流動支付服務，但不使用服務的主因包括安全性考慮（68%）、現有付款方法足夠（30%）及操作困難（27%）。<br />\n<br />\n該中心於9月訪問600名50至69歲的人士，結果發現，43%受訪者認為嶄新的金融科技服務是為年輕人而設，並不適合中老年人。同時他們亦擔心若自己未能配合金融科技的發展，可以選擇的金融服務類型會受到限制。<br />\n<br />\n在常見的金融科技服務中，65%受訪者表示在過去12個月内曾使用流動支付服務，當中50至59歲的受訪者使用率較高，達76%，反觀60至69歲長者的使用率只有47%。其他科技方面，45%受訪者曾使用雙重認證技術，但只有18%曾使用生物辨識認證，如指紋、臉部或聲音辨識等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，36%受訪者認為金融科技服務難以使用，不過若向他們提供示範和指導，有61%受訪者表示有信心嘗試使用服務，但仍有14%不想試用。<br />\n<br />\n投資者教育中心總經理李博衞先生指，年長人士對新科技不熟悉和缺乏信心，令他們對金融科技卻步，故應加強教育及制定保護措施，避免長者誤墮騙局。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2213439/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A65-%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%9B%BE%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2213439%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25EF%25BC%259A65-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=RX7ZHns07AflqApY6FlLgcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=183de90e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2213439/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A65-%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%9B%BE%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98?mtc=20023</a>"},{"pid":"53a0e88f119f5e96080d7bab8584d4817c23a350","tid":910594,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:10:01.000Z","msg":"喔喔<br />\n老正見到呢篇文章實開心死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c7f94732f97bf1ffbcd15db5eb99c7c5c54668","tid":910594,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"又想洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八達通係咪流動支付呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80e947fce87bc01666a4ed1d87b129566bedfad","tid":910594,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99c7f94732f97bf1ffbcd15db5eb99c7c5c54668","tid":910594,"uid":153418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"又想洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八達通係咪流動支付呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"信用卡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1f8e61517ff9757a6562a7793dc9bc3f42f178","tid":910594,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"微信搵妓師"},{"pid":"b3d5e479a2131685461f51361520faea2b663f95","tid":910594,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:00:39.000Z","msg":"擔心大阿哥"},{"pid":"4fa8a4d291b346daedac3de9ca9a5ee90a3219a6","tid":910594,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"QR code D落後既電子支付就咪用黎扮新野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}